The paper deals with image-based 3D face reconstruction, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of 3D morphable model (3DMM) and generative adversarial network (GAN) also suggests that the paper may belong to graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. The paper also involves machine learning techniques such as convolutional neural network (CNN), which falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
